				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12652581/scp-4358#post-4419165</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 09 Nov 2019 21:08:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Altered Nova</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>81815</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The O5 members must be extraordinarily busy people to directly supervise the containment procedures of over 4000 anomalies.</p> <p>Does the ethics committee have any real power in your foundation? What do they do if they feel the O5 command is being unnecessarily cruel to cut costs to a severe enough degree to not be worth the tradeoff?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12652581#post-4416050</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12652581/scp-4358#post-4416050</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2019 00:14:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>kinchtheknifeblade</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1345012</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
