						 <p>It's a fun little SCP, but I feel like I must have missed some subtle implication that the anomaly is actually far more dangerous or important than it appears to be. Otherwise why would the O5 council care enough about it to bother overruling the ethics committee on the containment procedures?</p> 
				 	]]>
