					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12652581#post-4392827</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12652581/scp-4358#post-4392827</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2019 16:50:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>peppermint_legos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5515758</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>My bigger gripe is that I don't really see why O5 would get involved at all.</p> <p>It's a tiny section of ground in Ohio that makes people act out for 16 hours at a time &#8212; it's a great SCP, but it's an *unimportant* one. No way did all 13 Overseers gather to vote on this: they have bigger fish to fry.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
